{"tid":2297202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★據報美國政府將限制89間與軍方有關中國企業","createTime":"2020-11-23T06:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T07:31:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2687c492a02c4ba4e11ab668b948c1e55278e9e3","tid":2297202,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:07:47.000Z","msg":"美國政府計劃宣布，限制89間被指與軍方有關聯的中國企業。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述消息報道，這89間中國企業，涉及中國航天及其他領域，將限制這些企業，採購美國一系列產品及技術。<br />\n<br />\n據報名單上的企業，包括中國商用飛機公司、中國航空工業集團及10間關聯實體。<br />\n<br />\n分析認為，若果美國政府公布有關企業名單，將令中美貿易關係更加緊張，亦衝擊向中國出售民用航空零部件的美國企業及其他產業。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561425-20201123.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561425-20201123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnQmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=24fabdf2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561425-20201123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5d9a821a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561425-20201123.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"202321c670b21cd6b8003c8c92a6686e18049202","tid":2297202,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:08:22.000Z","msg":"買中呢d 股票drop to $0<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab9b1dce44e29556126fe2891bc6a342c547976","tid":2297202,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/d